{"tid":1983052,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"謎樣生物一身金毛「像熊又像獅子」　保育員卻說牠超溫柔","createTime":"2020-04-21T14:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T14:26:47.000Z","uid":32511,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5fe64be4e834c40990aae729151bfb1380858c3d","tid":1983052,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/N2c3mei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FN2c3mei.jpg&h=640d76c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這隻動物一身金毛，頭頸部則是一圈黑棕色澎毛，乍看長得像獅子，卻又長著一張圓滾滾的熊臉。原來，牠是來自柬埔寨的亞洲黑熊(moon bear)「布蘭蒂(Brandy)」，特別的長相在網路上引發討論，還有人以為是合成照呢！<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KHy9juI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKHy9juI.jpg&h=d3ef644b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保育團體Free the Bears表示，布蘭蒂於1999年在柬埔寨南部一處樹林裡被人發現，當時該林區正準備開發改種植棕櫚樹，牠無助地緊靠在一棵樹上，因此被救援來到Free the Bears經營的柬埔寨熊保護區，一直被照顧到現在。雖然有著神獸般的珍稀外表，但照顧布蘭蒂的保育員說，牠是一隻特別溫柔的熊，時常讓人感到驚喜和快樂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qd4SK9u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fqd4SK9u.jpg&h=d526ae07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n布蘭蒂的照片被分享到臉書一科學粉絲專頁，不到一天就累積3.4萬讚，並有超過7000次分享。許多網友留言，「為什麼大家要一直稱這頭獅子為熊呢？明明就是獅子嘛！」、「這是一頭間諜獅子」、「如果在古代可能會被說是獅子和熊生出的神獸」。"},{"pid":"fa9973a83bc7d744494798233a39669f922b63a6","tid":1983052,"uid":147916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:22:55.000Z","msg":"乜撚野嚟㗎屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peoSq06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpeoSq06.jpg&h=638f5202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1aYmzs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1aYmzs.jpg&h=02f446fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kti3xF8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkti3xF8.jpg&h=f65b9aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDM8JNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDM8JNX.jpg&h=d22d7406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sh96vs0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsh96vs0.jpg&h=69abff0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzcLL1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzcLL1n.jpg&h=6ce07bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32T3xGo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32T3xGo.jpg&h=3d7fd808&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baae9c54a034af43c97b4b830eddb4b4f5dc6bfb","tid":1983052,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:23:50.000Z","msg":"獅子屌咗隻熊"},{"pid":"07c5570febd04730d176768b718744bd2f0c8f57","tid":1983052,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:26:47.000Z","msg":"最後果張有d似小櫻隻寵物基路仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}